snippet.title: Shootout - Official Announcement Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Check out the gameplay trailer for Shootout, an intense VR arena shooter with over 900 weapon combinations! An open alpha is coming to Meta Quest 2 summer 2023.
